#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:3
msgid "Software RAID device"
msgstr "軟體 RAID 裝置"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:7
msgid "Configure software RAID"
msgstr "設定軟體 RAID"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:12
msgid "Write the changes to the storage devices and configure RAID?"
msgstr "是否要將變更寫入儲存裝置中並設定 RAID？"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:12
msgid ""
"Before RAID can be configured, the changes have to be written to the storage "
"devices.  These changes cannot be undone."
msgstr ""
"必須先將這些變更寫入儲存裝置中，然後才能對 RAID 進行設定。這些變更將無法還"
"原。"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:12
msgid ""
"When RAID is configured, no additional changes to the partitions in the "
"disks containing physical volumes are allowed.  Please convince yourself "
"that you are satisfied with the current partitioning scheme in these disks."
msgstr ""
"一旦 RAID 設定完成，就不能再對磁碟中包含了 Physical Volume 的分割區進行任何額"
"外的變更了。因此，在繼續之前請確認您是否已滿意於目前這些磁碟所採取的分割方"
"式。"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:12
msgid "${ITEMS}"
msgstr "${ITEMS}"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:26
msgid "RAID configuration failure"
msgstr "RAID 的設定失敗了"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:26
msgid "An error occurred while writing the changes to the storage devices."
msgstr "在將變更寫入儲存裝置時發生錯誤。"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:26
msgid "The configuration of RAID is aborted."
msgstr "RAID 的設定作業已經中止。"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:33
msgid "physical volume for RAID"
msgstr "RAID 的 Physical Volume"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:37
msgid "raid"
msgstr "raid"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:42
msgid "Really use software RAID?"
msgstr "是否確定要使用軟體 RAID？"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:42
msgid ""
"Debian does not currently support using software RAID for the root "
"filesystem or /boot partition. A system installed in this way will not boot."
msgstr ""
"Debian 目前並不支援在 root 檔案系統或是在 /boot 分割區上使用軟體 RAID。以此方"
"式安裝的系統將會無法開機。"

#~ msgid "Use the partition as a RAID device"
#~ msgstr "將此分割區作為 RAID 裝置"

#~ msgid "Confirm whether you are ready to configure RAID."
#~ msgstr "請確認您是否真的已準備好要設定 RAID。"
